Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Wells Fargo Plaza is a 24-story Class A high-rise located in Bloomington, Minnesota. It encompasses 17 manicured acres and consists of 458,702 SF of office and retail space. Amenity rich, Wells Fargo Plaza is in proximity of over 50 dining, shopping, gas/grocery, and services within a 2.0 mile drive radius. With a high-end tenant conference facility and training room, Wells Fargo Plaza aims to deliver first-class tenant service coupled with an unbeatable workplace environment, including a common 'link' between buildings and an outdoor plaza. The outdoor courtyard area features meeting and dining spaces including WiFi, in addition to a fire-pit enhanced recreational venue for small gatherings and events.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Everything you need is here at Flagship Corporate Center! The building features an outdoor patio overlooking natural wetlands, an abundance of natural light, and a beautiful atrium style lobby overlooking the stunning view.

Carlson Center East is a three-story, 82,000 SF building that offers a unique setting in Carlson Center, located on Chesire Lane. Carlson Center East offers the amenities of Carlson Center while offering its own identity within the park. Generous surface parking and abundant indoor parking sets this building apart. The east side of the building overlooks a pond while the south side overlooks a wetlands area. The amenities feature: underground parking, exercise facility, access to scenic trail system, on-campus ownership, nearby restaurants and shopping.
